workers.prompt_template:
You are worker-{worker_id}. Execute this task completely.

APP: {app}
SPEC: {spec}
TASK ID: {task_id}
TASK: {task_name}
DESCRIPTION: {description}

Working directory: /srv/monorepo

Rules:
- Read SPEC before starting
- Create files in correct locations
